---
/* Pricing Section — Split layout | Light Editorial */
---

<section id="tarifs" class="bg-surface py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)]">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="asymmetric-grid items-center">

      <!-- Left: Benefits (5 cols) -->
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold mb-8 tracking-tighter text-on-surface reveal">INVESTIR<br />DANS TON <span class="text-primary">AVENIR</span></h2>
        <ul class="space-y-6 reveal delay-1">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface-variant">Accès à vie à la plateforme et aux futures mises à jour.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface-variant">24 sessions live en groupe avec Lilian.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface-variant">2h de coaching individuel personnalisé.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface-variant">Communauté privée d'indépendants chevronnés.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
            <span class="text-on-surface-variant">SaaS de pilotage freelance inclus.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Pricing card (7 cols) -->
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="relative p-12 bg-white border border-outline-variant/30 shadow-2xl shadow-on-surface/5 overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/5 blur-3xl rounded-full translate-x-16 -translate-y-16" aria-hidden="true"></div>

          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-12 reveal">
            <div>
              <div class="font-sans text-primary text-xs font-bold tracking-widest mb-2 uppercase">Tarif Early Adopter</div>
              <div class="text-6xl font-display font-bold text-on-surface">1&nbsp;500&euro;</div>
              <div class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant line-through mt-1">3&nbsp;000&euro;</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <div class="text-[10px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant tracking-[0.2em] mb-1 font-bold uppercase">Disponibilité</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-display text-error font-bold">6 PLACES MAXIMUM</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-md reveal delay-1">
            Le prix d'une <strong>liberté totale</strong>. Rentabilisé dès ton <strong>premier contrat</strong> d'indépendant augmenté.
          </p>

          <p class="text-primary text-sm font-medium mb-8 reveal delay-1">
            Paiement en 3 fois disponible
          </p>

          <a
            href="https://cal.com/lilian-sevoumian/30min"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="w-full py-6 bg-primary text-white font-display font-black text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter hover:brightness-110 active:scale-[0.98] transition-all shadow-lg shadow-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md reveal delay-2"
          >
            RÉSERVER MA PLACE MAINTENANT
          </a>

          <p class="text-center mt-5 text-on-surface-variant text-sm reveal delay-3">
            La seule formation qui s'occupe de toi, pas seulement de vendre.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
